OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FUK's last opencast coal    
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fmine shuts after legal row 
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, The UK's last opencast coalmine -      
OL,6, dubbed a "neighbour from hell" - will  
OL,7, close on Thursday as fears mount over  
OL,8, whether the huge site will be restored.
OL,10,FDocuments seen by BBC News show        
OL,11,Fconcerns at the Welsh government and UK
OL,12,FCoal Authority that Merthyr Tydfil's   
OL,13,FFfos-y-Fran mine may be abandoned.     
OL,15,FEstimated clean-up costs have grown to 
OL,16,Fbetween #120m and #175m.               
OL,18,FSite operator Merthyr (South Wales) Ltd
OL,19,Fsaid it was in "constructive dialogue" 
OL,20,Fwith Merthyr Tydfil council.           
